bilingual.source: He came to pick me up personally.
He always personally sees off the guests.
The boss likes to personally give orders.

bilingual.target: 他亲自为这个错误道歉。

bilingual.source: We need to personally experience this process.
bilingual.target: 我们需要亲自体会这个过程。

yingyinNormal.en: Uh, no, not yet. There's still a few people I haven't told personally.
yingyinNormal.zh: 还没有，几个人我还没亲自告诉他们。

yingyinNormal.en: Yeah, but I think the Machine wants you to handle this one personally.
yingyinNormal.zh: 好吧，但我看机器想要你亲自处理这个号码。

yingyinNormal.en: They request you personally, Sire. Perhaps a ruse to take your life.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他们要求您亲自出席，陛下，也许是想取您性命。

yingyinNormal.en: I personally have shooed a homeless man away from peeing on that shrine twice.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我亲自赶走了一个流浪汉不让他往神龛上撒尿，赶了两次啊。

yingyinNormal.en: I'm also going to meet later tonight with Mr. Mahmoud privately. To personally apologize.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我今晚还准备私下见默罕默德先生，亲自向他道歉。

yingyinNormal.en: If you're found in an area not designated to your gender, I will personally neuter you! Am I clear?
yingyinNormal.zh: 如果你发现哪个地方和你性别不符，我会亲自来抹去你的性别，清楚了吗？

yingyinNormal.en: Prepped and ready, sir. Given the severity of the situation, I figured you'd want to see her personally.
yingyinNormal.zh: 已经准备好了，先生，鉴于情况的严重程度，我觉得您会希望亲自见她。

yingyinNormal.en: I, personally, will see to it that your organs are removed and placed in separate jewel-encrusted jars. Thank you.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我，将亲自监督你的内脏被移除并分别放入镶满宝石的罐子里。谢谢。
yingyinNormal.videoNameEn: 《Night at the Museum: Secret of the Tomb》

yingyinNormal.en: The director of the CIA called me inquiring about you personally. Of course to protect your cover, I had to lie.
yingyinNormal.zh: 中情局局长亲自向我询问过你的事，为了保护你的卧底身份，我当然只能撒谎。

yingyinNormal.en: Theresa may have been trying to use the woodcutter as a mule, and when that failed, then may have tried to do the transfer personally.
yingyinNormal.zh: 特蕾莎或许之前想利用伐木工代劳，但后来失败了，她便想亲自来完成传输。

yingyinNormal.en: Well, that's why you're here, isn't it? To assist with our repairs? Why else would the head of Starfleet personally come to the edge of the Neutral Zone?
yingyinNormal.zh: 我想这就是您来这里的原因，没错吧? 来帮助我们维修？不然为什么联盟的高官会亲自来到中立区的边缘地带?

yingyinNormal.en: I'd like to take a moment to personally thank Dr. Amy Farrah Fowler, who you may or may not know is the first woman to co-host a flag or banner-related Internet info-tainment show.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我想花一点时间亲自谢谢艾米·费拉·福勒博士，你们或许知道，也或许不知道，她是第一位搭档主持关于旗帜或横幅相关的网络寓教于乐节目的女性。

yingyinNormal.en: This is a challenge I take personally.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这对于我来说是一个挑战。

yingyinNormal.en: Personally, I'm going to stay in the boat.
yingyinNormal.zh: 要是我，还是呆在船上为好。
yingyinNormal.videoNameZh: 《大卫·贝克汉姆：探索未知之境》

yingyinNormal.en: But I would personally appreciate it as a personal favor to me, personally, if we just worked together, just us, tricks and all.
yingyinNormal.zh: 可我想跟你说的是，当然这个主意有点自私，如果我们两个能联起手来，再弄点小伎俩。

yingyinNormal.en: You can't take that personally. How else is she supposed to take it?
yingyinNormal.zh: 你千万别多想。那让她还能怎么想？

yingyinNormal.en: You just don't have the money or the reputation. Don't take it personally.
yingyinNormal.zh: 只是因为你们钱不够多，名不够响，别太当回事。

yingyinNormal.en: I do not personally understand why it has anything to do with the poor uncle!
yingyinNormal.zh: 我不太明白可怜的舅舅跟这有哪门子关系。

yingyinNormal.en: Yes. But this is not a Lockhart/Gardner invoice. This has been issued by you personally.
yingyinNormal.zh: 对。但这不是洛&加律所的发票，是由你个人签发的。

yingyinNormal.en: I accept your challenge, if only to personally ripped the heart out of your pathetic body.
yingyinNormal.zh: 如果只是私人的，我接受你的挑战，我将撕开你可怜的身体，取出你的心脏。
